column2: "Since we managed to run into you, I'd like to give you some information but today we don't have any!"
"We're scrambling to look for some more, but haven't come up with anything. Next time we'll definitely have some!"
"Sorry, it seems we don't have any leads at the moment."
"There aren't too many people who specialize in it, and not too many who recognize the importance either."
"Well, actually Patty was told to stop, but she's not the kind of person to give up."
"Sorry for wasting your time, I'm going to chase after my worthless sister."
